<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .otp-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            background: #f8f9ff;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px dashed #667eea;
            display: inline-block;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #0c5460;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .support-link {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .support-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .otp-code {
                font-size: 28px;
                padding: 15px 20px;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üîê</div>
            <h1>Email Verification</h1>
            <p>Please verify your email address to continue</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{firstName}},</h2>
            
            <p>Thank you for registering with <strong>Resume Refresh Platform</strong>! To complete your account setup and ensure the security of your account, please verify your email address using the code below:</p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
                <p><strong>Enter this code in the verification form</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="expiry-notice">
                <strong>‚è∞ Important:</strong> This verification code will expire in <strong>{{expiryMinutes}} minutes</strong>. Please use it as soon as possible.
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                <strong>üõ°Ô∏è Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't request this verification code, please ignore this email. Your account remains secure.
            </div>
            
            <h3>What happens next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Enter the verification code on the registration page</li>
                <li>Complete your profile setup</li>
                <li>Start exploring job opportunities or posting jobs</li>
                <li>Get personalized AI-powered recommendations</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you're having trouble with the verification process, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Resume Refresh Platform</strong></p>
            <p>Your AI-powered career advancement partner</p>
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="support-link">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #adb5bd;">
                This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
